{"tid":2096674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【8.25 荃灣衝突】中大男生被指推倒警員脫罪　官拒接納受襲警證供","createTime":"2020-07-06T09:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T12:54:36.000Z","uid":56115,"like":526,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"14a416326d7ab796805d965895cbcb3c76473638","tid":2096674,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"去年 8 月 25 日的「葵荃青遊行」衝突中，一名中大男學生被指推向防暴警員盾牌，使其跌倒。他早前否認一項襲警罪受審，今日（6 日）在西九龍裁判法院獲裁定罪名<span style=\"color: red;\">不成立</span>。裁判官指，聲稱受襲警員指控被告用手推其盾牌，但片段顯示他倒地後大叫「你 kick 我！」，明言推與踢是兩個截然不同的動作，感覺不應混淆，認為警員的<span style=\"color: red;\">口供存疑</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/8-25-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%80%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98%E6%8B%92%E6%8E%A5%E7%B4%8D%E5%8F%97%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-25-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2580%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25B4%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%2F&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=bf6647b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-25-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2580%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25B4%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%2F&h=8156444d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandn